title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 26 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 26 2022
description:
Flip-Flop Fauci! 2022: Fauci on school lockdowns: "I didn't recommend locking anything down." Flashback: In October, 2020 Fauci said "I recommended to the president that we shut the country down." Fauci is the most destructive bureaucrat in American history. "Health Propaganda Czar" Ashish Jha: "Most deaths are happening in people who are not up to date with their vaccines." Dr. Marty Makary of Johns Hopkins University and author of The Price We Pay, joins Clay and Buck for a covid update, why the bureaucrats can't admit mistakes, the dangers of constant masking and Big Pharma's push for new vaccinations.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
